<figureCitation box="[767,805,662,688]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="6.[189,232,1921,1947]" captionTargetBox="[201,1393,1370,1855]" captionTargetId="figure@6.[189,1399,1344,1865]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="Fig. 3. Photomicrographs of male periphallic organs. A. D. seguyi Smart, 1945 (MNHN). B. D. aff. tsacasi Bock &amp; Wheeler, 1972 (MNHN). C. D. mylenae David &amp; Yassin sp. nov. (MNHN). Scale bars = 0.1 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3251575/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">3A</figureCitation>
